attr.title: I Gacha Head
attr.desc: A puzzle game where the top of your head falls off when you walk into low platforms.
attr.inst: Download the IGachaHeadBuild5.zip (Newest Version) version for free at itch.io (https://dylanbrowngames.itch.io/i-gacha-head). Extract the .zip, and copy the game files to this port's gamedata folder.
attr.inst_md: Download the *IGachaHeadBuild5.zip (Newest Version)* version for free at [itch.io](https://dylanbrowngames.itch.io/i-gacha-head). Extract the *.zip*, and copy the game files file to this port's *gamedata* folder.
